{"id": "art-372", "label": "Art. 372", "title": "Art. 372: Efectele faţă de terţi", "slug": "art-372", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 372: Efectele fa&#355;&#259; de ter&#355;i </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)Creditorii so&#355;ilor nu pot\ncere separa&#355;ia de bunuri, dar pot interveni în cauz&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(2)Dispozi&#355;iile art. 369 alin.\n(3) &#351;i (4) se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>CAPITOLUL VII:Desfacerea c&#259;s&#259;toriei</span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA 1:Cazurile de divor&#355;</span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:\nnormal'><span style='color:black'>SUBSEC&#354;IUNEA 1:Dispozi&#355;ii generale</span></b></p>"}